  <brief_title>Vagifem® Used for the Treatment of Atrophic Vaginitis Due to Oestrogen Deficiency</brief_title>
  <official_title>Vagifem® Used for the Treatment of Atrophic Vaginitis Due to Oestrogen Deficiency</official_title>
